🍽️ Recipe App


📖 Overview
The Recipe App is a simple web application that allows users to search for recipes by dish name. It fetches data from the TheMealDB API and displays the recipe details to the user.

✨ Features

🔍 User-friendly interface with a search bar to input dish names.

📋 Fetches and displays recipe data from TheMealDB API.

📱 Responsive design for optimal viewing on various devices.

🛠️ Technologies Used


HTML: For the structure of the web application.
CSS: For styling the application.
JavaScript: For handling user interactions and fetching data from the API.


🚀 Getting Started
Clone the repository to your local machine.
Open the index.html file in your browser to run the app.


📦 Installation
No additional installation is required. Just open the index.html file in your favorite browser.




